    <div id="root"></div>
    
    <script type="text/babel">
        // Paste the React component code here
        // Then add at the bottom:
        ReactDOM.render(<SecurityDashboard />, document.getElementById('root'));
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

**Save this as `security_gui.html` and open in a browser!**

