## ğŸ”§ API Endpoints (for developers)

### **GET /api/status**
Get current scan status
```json
{
  "running": false,
  "progress": 100,
  "current_phase": "Scan Complete",
  "findings": [...],
  "stats": { ... },
  "logs": [...]
}
```

### **GET /api/system-info**
Get system information
```json
{
  "os": "Linux",
  "hostname": "myserver",
  "uptime_days": 45.2,
  "memory_gb": 16.0
}
```

### **POST /api/scan**
Start a new scan
```json
{
  "target": "localhost",
  "type": "full"  // or "system", "network", "config"
}
```

### **POST /api/remediate**
Apply remediation
```json
{
  "finding_id": "SYS-0001"
}
```

### **GET /api/export**
Export complete report as JSON

