## ğŸ¯ Scan Types Explained

### **Full Scan** (Recommended)
- âœ… System update check
- âœ… Firewall status
- âœ… SSH configuration audit
- âœ… Open ports scan
- âœ… System uptime check
- â±ï¸ Duration: ~30 seconds

### **System Scan**
- âœ… Available security updates
- âœ… Kernel version check
- âœ… System uptime
- â±ï¸ Duration: ~10 seconds

### **Network Scan**
- âœ… Open ports discovery
- âœ… Service detection
- âœ… Listening services
- â±ï¸ Duration: ~15 seconds

### **Config Scan**
- âœ… Firewall configuration
- âœ… SSH hardening check
- âœ… Security settings audit
- â±ï¸ Duration: ~5 seconds

